Author: Nikos Mavrogiannopoulos <nmav@gnutls.org>
Date:   Tue Mar 31 07:40:21 2020 +0200

    NEWS: updated for release
    
    Signed-off-by: Nikos Mavrogiannopoulos <nmav@gnutls.org>

