    Signed-off-by: Tim Rühsen <tim.ruehsen@gmx.de>

Author: Tim Rühsen <tim.ruehsen@gmx.de>
Date:   Thu Dec 19 11:48:47 2019 +0100

    status_request.c: Silence -Wsign-compare
    
    Signed-off-by: Tim Rühsen <tim.ruehsen@gmx.de>

Author: Tim Rühsen <tim.ruehsen@gmx.de>
Date:   Thu Dec 19 11:46:23 2019 +0100

