Date:   Sat Sep 28 14:28:12 2019 +0200

    Regenerate asm files with -fPIC
    
    CRYPTOGAMS' perl-scripts can produce different output if -fPIC is passed
    as option. Set -fPIC for the same files as openssl does.
    
    Closes #818
    
