Author: Nikos Mavrogiannopoulos <nmav@gnutls.org>
Date:   Tue Dec 1 10:40:23 2015 +0100

    tools: don't compile tpmtool if PKCS11 is disabled
    
    That is because GnuTLS' TPM code makes use of the PKCS11 PIN callbacks.

